
'''Adaakoye Afahy'''ɛ '''y'''ɛ Otwa afahyɛ a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Gurunsi ɛwɔ Bolgatanga ne Zuaungu a ɛwɔ Atifi Apuei Mantam wɔ Ghana no di<ref>https://flygoldstar.com/tour-packages-uppereast-region.html</ref>. Wodi afahye yi wo bosome a eto edikan ne nea eto so mienu no mu<ref>http://h2829516.stratoserver.net/tourism/index.html</ref> <ref>https://ghananation.com/tourism/The-Upper-East-Region.php</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Aheno ne, wɔn manfo no dwa data wɔ afehyɛ no bere mu. Woyi apaye ma wɔn abosom no. Wɔsan nso o twene di asa <ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref>.

== Mfaso ==
Wodi afahyɛ no de da wɔn abosom ase sɛ w’ama wɔn otwa bere papa<ref>https://touringghana.com/upper-west-region/</ref>.

